               stealing, on the <rs id="t18270913-210-cd1184" type="crimeDate">14th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-210-off1183 t18270913-210-cd1184"></join>, 1 watch, value 30s.; 2 seals, value 6s., and 1 key, value 1s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18270913-210-victim1869" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
                        Larke
                     <interp inst="t18270913-210-victim1869" type="surname" value="Larke"></interp>
